{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847421803,"sessionID":"ses_2873f106fffeCtaB3PNA0dSVhZ","part":{"id":"prt_d78c12747001VBxpRzuZp6Y7pZ","messageID":"msg_d78c116eb001nQgUAvBTPjTHXe","sessionID":"ses_2873f106fffeCtaB3PNA0dSVhZ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_32a0f87221b84bb89e5b0d81","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/router  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: **Stage:** ST-1 (Spec)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Core Implementation\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Implement proxy core\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Add route matching\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Implement request forwarding\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ## Phase 2: Verification\n19: \n20: - [ ] **2.1** `go build ./pkg/router/...` — successful compilation\n21: - [ ] **2.2** `go test ./pkg/router/...` — all unit tests pass\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## References\n26: \n27: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-009/delta-spec.md`\n\n(End of file - total 27 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/router  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-1 (Spec)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Implementation\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Implement proxy core\n- [ ] **1.2** Add route matching\n- [ ] **1.3** Implement request forwarding\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Verification\n\n- [ ] **2.1** `go build ./pkg/router/...` — successful compilation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775847421791,"end":1775847421800}}}}
