{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775847424552,"sessionID":"ses_2873f106fffeCtaB3PNA0dSVhZ","part":{"id":"prt_d78c14226001uGTnpurtAf6WW7","messageID":"msg_d78c137a40019U8TjZntQ1736n","sessionID":"ses_2873f106fffeCtaB3PNA0dSVhZ","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847450572,"sessionID":"ses_2873f106fffeCtaB3PNA0dSVhZ","part":{"id":"prt_d78c14dba001Scv7FOF6VSjxNZ","messageID":"msg_d78c137a40019U8TjZntQ1736n","sessionID":"ses_2873f106fffeCtaB3PNA0dSVhZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_de70a531cb4b4685b0ffd47f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/router  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Implementation)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Infrastructure\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/router/config.go` — Config struct with defaults (listen `:8080`, backend timeout `30s`, idle timeout `60s`, health check `10s`)\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/router/server.go` — Router struct with Start/Shutdown methods\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/router/backend.go` — Backend pool management (add/remove/update endpoints)\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/router/proxy.go` — Reverse proxy implementation with httputil\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Kubernetes Informers\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/router/informer.go` — Setup AgentRuntime informer with namespace filtering\n- [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/router/informer.go` — Setup CodeInterpreter informer with namespace filtering\n- [ ] **2.3** Implement `addAgentRuntime()` handler — Add endpoint when AgentRuntime phase=Running\n- [ ] **2.4** Implement `updateAgentRuntime()` handler — Update endpoint on status change\n- [ ] **2.5** Implement `deleteAgentRuntime()` handler — Remove endpoint on CR deletion\n- [ ] **2.6** Implement `addCodeInterpreter()` handler — Add endpoint when CodeInterpreter phase=Running\n- [ ] **2.7** Implement `updateCodeInterpreter()` handler — Update endpoint on status change\n- [ ] **2.8** Implement `deleteCodeInterpreter()` handler — Remove endpoint on CR deletion\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Routing Logic\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Create `pkg/router/route.go` — Path prefix matching (e.g., `/agent/` → backend)\n- [ ] **3.2** Create `pkg/router/route.go` — Header-based routing (X-Backend, Content-Type)\n- [ ] **3.3** Implement 404 response for unmatched paths\n- [ ] **3.4** Implement query parameter preservation in routing\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Health Checking\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Create `pkg/router/health.go` — Periodic health check scheduler\n- [ ] **4.2** Implement health check request with 5s timeout\n- [ ] **4.3** Implement unhealthy backend removal (3 consecutive failures)\n- [ ] **4.4** Implement backend recovery (mark healthy on success)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Connection Pooling\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Configure httputil.ReverseProxy with Transport for keep-alive\n- [ ] **5.2** Implement max connections per backend limit (default 100)\n- [ ] **5.3** Implement idle connection cleanup (idleTimeout)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Middleware\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/router/ratelimit.go` — Token bucket rate limiting (enable/disable)\n- [ ] **6.2** Create `pkg/router/auth.go` — Bearer token validation middleware\n- [ ] **6.3** Create `pkg/router/logging.go` — Request/response logging middleware\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Metrics\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Implement `router_request_duration_seconds` histogram\n- [ ] **7.2** Implement `router_backend_requests_total` counter\n- [ ] **7.3** Implement `router_backend_healthy` gauge\n- [ ] **7.4** Implement `router_errors_total` counter\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Verification\n\n- [ ] **8.1** `go build ./pkg/router/...` — successful compilation\n- [ ] **8.2** `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` — all unit tests pass\n- [ ] **8.3** Integration test: Router starts, discovers CRs, routes requests\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `k8s.io/client-go/informers` — Kubernetes informers\n- `k8s.io/client-go/listers` — CR listers\n- `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` — Metrics\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-009/delta-spec.md`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775847450557,"end":1775847450569}}}}
